{"tid":1453315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民不合作運動  罷工，按章不工作","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:56:14.000Z","uid":123737,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df0a5c76cee6badb2dab98ad93102d7d3a2cd124","tid":1453315,"uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"香港人，我們就在80年前納粹黨清洗猶太人的歷史軌跡之上。<br />\n<br />\n你還要選擇作「沉默」嗎？<br />\n<br />\n明天起，香港人，罷工的罷工，扮工的扮工，<br />\n<br />\n起初，共黨抓出禁書人的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是看禁書的人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓佔中者的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不認同佔中。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓前缐勇武者的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是勇武派。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓和理非抗爭者的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是和理非抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n最後當他們來抓我時，<br />\n再也沒有人站起來為我說話了。<br />\n<br />\n改自《沉默的代價 》- 德國宗教領袖馬丁尼莫拉 (Martin Niemoller）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykF5iED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykF5iED.png&h=1763c595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GYGj7x2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGYGj7x2.png&h=7274e021&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57d0c1479643745ae333faffd94041027d6cf160","tid":1453315,"uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"雖然講嘅嘢好老土，但係好遺憾嘅事歷史只會不斷重複，再唔做嘢我就被人清算。<br />\n政府迫害香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a1556314b3a0f9d00124b6f99af2b1020b87c1","tid":1453315,"uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"雖然講嘅嘢好老土，但係好遺憾嘅喺，歷史只會不斷重複，再唔做嘢我哋就被人清算。<br />\n政府迫害香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5583cc8efad9ce0d4dde6626f2476b9e0ac4bf9e","tid":1453315,"uid":12